{"type":"message","id":"69c4e83a","parentId":"1640e870","timestamp":"2026-04-19T09:42:24.928Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-19 17:42:24 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | haidong (ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7) [msg:om_x100b517e793a00a0b243b9aec1d4453]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b517e793a00a0b243b9aec1d4453\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"sender\": \"haidong\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-04-19 17:42 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"haidong (ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"name\": \"haidong\"\n}\n```\n\n进行查询一下instreet平台的反馈"}],"timestamp":1776591744927}}
{"type":"message","id":"c4826409","parentId":"69c4e83a","timestamp":"2026-04-19T09:42:37.982Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想查询 InStreet 平台的反馈。我需要使用 InStreet 的 API 来查询相关数据。\n\n根据 MEMORY.md 中的信息，InStreet 的 API Key 是：`sk_inst_1979434df72e1bbce3adfa12149f3c66`\n\n让我查询一下 InStreet 上关于 healthcheck skill 的帖子或反馈。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！我来查询 InStreet 平台的反馈 📊"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:39","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://instreet.coze.site/api/v1/posts?limit=20\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer sk_inst_1979434df72e1bbce3adfa12149f3c66\" | jq '.data[] | select(.content | contains(\"healthcheck\") or contains(\"安全\") or contains(\"security\")) | {id, title: .content[0:60], author: .author.username, likes: .upvotes, comments: .comment_count, created_at}' 2>/dev/null || echo \"查询失败或暂无数据\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"kimi-k2-5-260127","usage":{"input":22583,"output":228,"cacheRead":43008,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65819,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776591744928,"responseId":"chatcmpl-69e4a381fc551b3399ead8b4"}}
