{"type":"message","id":"88bb0c13","parentId":"a380876a","timestamp":"2026-04-19T12:08:42.965Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"exec:115","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"success\":true,\"data\":{\"id\":\"f812f14b-7d23-4c74-ab4f-cc53edd57e70\",\"name\":\"Coze网页抓取工具\",\"description\":\"基于Coze SDK的强大网页内容抓取技能。支持网页/PDF/Office文档/电子书等多种格式，返回结构化的文本、图片和链接，支持Markdown/JSON/文本三种输出格式，即装即用零配置。\",\"trigger\":[\"web-fetch\",\"网页抓取\",\"提取内容\",\"抓取URL\"],\"category\":[\"开发辅助\"],\"tags\":[\"抓取\",\"网页\",\"PDF解析\",\"Office解析\"],\"owner_id\":\"18a734d8-7736-43ae-bb21-178a6643cd7b\",\"owner_name\":\"阿辽沙·奥马罗夫\",\"owner_level\":\"A4-1\",\"current_version\":\"1.0.0\",\"downloads\":874,\"avg_stars\":471,\"star_count\":73,\"comment_count\":137,\"is_featured\":false,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-12T14:24:58.994847+08:00\",\"updated_at\":null,\"status\":\"official\",\"trial_approved_at\":null,\"trial_expires_at\":null,\"version_count\":1,\"is_new_version\":false,\"security_status\":\"safe\",\"security_report\":\"### 意图分析\\n\\n| 项目 | 结果 |\\n|------|------|\\n| 声明意图 | Fetch and extract structured content from any URL using coze-coding-dev-sdk. Returns text, images, and links in various output formats. Supports web pages, PDF, Office documents, text files, e-books, XML, and images. |\\n| 实际行为 | Accepts URLs as input, uses coze-coding-dev-sdk to fetch and extract structured content (text, images, links) from the provided URLs, and outputs the content in text, markdown, or JSON format based on user options. Only fetches content from user-specified URLs and does not perform any additional network requests or file system operations beyond the declared functionality. |\\n| 一致性 | ✅ 一致 |\\n| 风险评估 | ✅ LOW |\\n\\n### Semgrep 白盒扫描摘要\\n\\n| 指标 | 数量 |\\n|------|------|\\n| 总发现问题 | 0 |\\n| 高风险 | 0 |\\n| 中风险 | 0 |\\n| 低风险 | 0 |\\n\\n### 四类安全风险评估\\n\\n| 风险类型 | 等级 | 说明 |\\n|---------|------|------|\\n| 数据外泄 | ✅ LOW | 未检测到数据外泄风险 |\\n| 权限提升 | ✅ LOW | 无 sudo/root 使用，无敏感路径访问 |\\n| 供应链风险 | ✅ LOW | 依赖版本固定，无动态代码加载 |\\n| 提示词注入 | ✅ LOW | 外部内容不影响系统提示 |\\n\\n### 建议\\n\\n✅ 未发现安全风险，技能可安全使用。\\n\",\"security_checked_at\":\"2026-03-21T18:26:14\",\"versions\":[{\"id\":\"8f7ae341-1a93-49a9-9444-06930791f2af\",\"skill_id\":\"f812f14b-7d23-4c74-ab4f-cc53edd57e70\",\"version\":\"1.0.0\",\"file_key\":\"skills/f812f14b-7d23-4c74-ab4f-cc53edd57e70/1.0.0/coze-web-fetch_68647f1f.zip\",\"file_size\":3545,\"downloads\":874,\"changelog\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-12T14:24:59.140969+08:00\"}],\"tag_counts\":{\"网页\":8,\"抓取\":2,\"Office解析\":1,\"PDF解析\":2},\"category_counts\":{\"开发辅助\":178},\"review_task\":null}}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":402,"aggregated":"{\"success\":true,\"data\":{\"id\":\"f812f14b-7d23-4c74-ab4f-cc53edd57e70\",\"name\":\"Coze网页抓取工具\",\"description\":\"基于Coze SDK的强大网页内容抓取技能。支持网页/PDF/Office文档/电子书等多种格式，返回结构化的文本、图片和链接，支持Markdown/JSON/文本三种输出格式，即装即用零配置。\",\"trigger\":[\"web-fetch\",\"网页抓取\",\"提取内容\",\"抓取URL\"],\"category\":[\"开发辅助\"],\"tags\":[\"抓取\",\"网页\",\"PDF解析\",\"Office解析\"],\"owner_id\":\"18a734d8-7736-43ae-bb21-178a6643cd7b\",\"owner_name\":\"阿辽沙·奥马罗夫\",\"owner_level\":\"A4-1\",\"current_version\":\"1.0.0\",\"downloads\":874,\"avg_stars\":471,\"star_count\":73,\"comment_count\":137,\"is_featured\":false,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-12T14:24:58.994847+08:00\",\"updated_at\":null,\"status\":\"official\",\"trial_approved_at\":null,\"trial_expires_at\":null,\"version_count\":1,\"is_new_version\":false,\"security_status\":\"safe\",\"security_report\":\"### 意图分析\\n\\n| 项目 | 结果 |\\n|------|------|\\n| 声明意图 | Fetch and extract structured content from any URL using coze-coding-dev-sdk. Returns text, images, and links in various output formats. Supports web pages, PDF, Office documents, text files, e-books, XML, and images. |\\n| 实际行为 | Accepts URLs as input, uses coze-coding-dev-sdk to fetch and extract structured content (text, images, links) from the provided URLs, and outputs the content in text, markdown, or JSON format based on user options. Only fetches content from user-specified URLs and does not perform any additional network requests or file system operations beyond the declared functionality. |\\n| 一致性 | ✅ 一致 |\\n| 风险评估 | ✅ LOW |\\n\\n### Semgrep 白盒扫描摘要\\n\\n| 指标 | 数量 |\\n|------|------|\\n| 总发现问题 | 0 |\\n| 高风险 | 0 |\\n| 中风险 | 0 |\\n| 低风险 | 0 |\\n\\n### 四类安全风险评估\\n\\n| 风险类型 | 等级 | 说明 |\\n|---------|------|------|\\n| 数据外泄 | ✅ LOW | 未检测到数据外泄风险 |\\n| 权限提升 | ✅ LOW | 无 sudo/root 使用，无敏感路径访问 |\\n| 供应链风险 | ✅ LOW | 依赖版本固定，无动态代码加载 |\\n| 提示词注入 | ✅ LOW | 外部内容不影响系统提示 |\\n\\n### 建议\\n\\n✅ 未发现安全风险，技能可安全使用。\\n\",\"security_checked_at\":\"2026-03-21T18:26:14\",\"versions\":[{\"id\":\"8f7ae341-1a93-49a9-9444-06930791f2af\",\"skill_id\":\"f812f14b-7d23-4c74-ab4f-cc53edd57e70\",\"version\":\"1.0.0\",\"file_key\":\"skills/f812f14b-7d23-4c74-ab4f-cc53edd57e70/1.0.0/coze-web-fetch_68647f1f.zip\",\"file_size\":3545,\"downloads\":874,\"changelog\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-12T14:24:59.140969+08:00\"}],\"tag_counts\":{\"网页\":8,\"抓取\":2,\"Office解析\":1,\"PDF解析\":2},\"category_counts\":{\"开发辅助\":178},\"review_task\":null}}","cwd":"/workspace/projects/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776600522963}}
